<h2 id="Syntax">Syntax</h2>
<pre class="twopartsyntaxbox"><a href="/en-US/docs/CSS/Value_definition_syntax" title="CSS/Value_definition_syntax">Formal syntax</a>: <code>auto <a href="/en-US/docs/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#Single_bar" title="Single bar: the two entities are optional, but exactly one must be present.">|</a> avoid</code>
</pre>
<pre>page-break-inside: auto
page-break-inside: avoid

page-break-inside: inherit
</pre>
<h3 id="Values">Values</h3>
<dl><dt>
  <code>auto</code></dt>
 <dd>
  Initial value. Automatic page breaks (neither forced nor forbidden).</dd>
 <dt>
  <code>avoid</code></dt>
 <dd>
  Avoid page breaks inside the element.</dd>
</dl><h3 id="Examples">Examples</h3>
<pre class="brush: css">/* avoid page break inside the paragraph */
p { page-break-inside: avoid;  } 
</pre>